Package <Unnamed>

Class Summary
ComplexOrder Class representing the decision to make a move/attack on a planet.
Conqueror A static-method helper class responsible for initiating battles on the opponent's planets.
Explorer A static-method class reponsible for capturing neutral planets.
Fleet Class representing a single fleet travelling between two planets.
MyBot This is the main class containing the body of the game Bot.
Oracle A static-method helper class responsible for predicting the outcomes of all future battles based on currently flying fleets.
Planet Class representing a single planet in the game.
PlanetWars Class representing the current game state.
Protector A static-method helper class containing methods for improving the defense of the player and moving defensive fleets.
Strategist A static-method helper class that contains methods for furthering long-term goals such as strategic position.
